          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y31A72D3-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">W</hi>HEN you censure the age,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y31A72D3-line-2" n="2">Be cautious and sage,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y31A72D3-line-3" n="3">Lest the courtiers offended should be;</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y31A72D3-line-4" n="4">If you mention vice or bribe,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-Y31A72D3-line-5" n="5">'Tis so pat to all the tribe,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-Y31A72D3-line-6" n="6">Each crys──── That was levell'd at me.</l>
          </lg>
